{"tid":513224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國第一女巨貪  色誘看守所副所長獲取方便","createTime":"2017-12-29T10:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T13:41:21.000Z","uid":76115,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"972bba3b4a47fa261eb01ae7dcb373a901ce4b6f","tid":513224,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:05:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.dwnews.com/china/big5/news/2017-12-29/60032626.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.dwnews.com%2Fchina%2Fbig5%2Fnews%2F2017-12-29%2F60032626.html&d=PyvhatFNHvf0VQZCNupr9pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=8da1438f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.dwnews.com/china/big5/news/2017-12-29/60032626.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中國三湘第一女巨貪蔣豔萍在看守所色誘副所長，為自己提供方便。 <br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體12月29日報道，蔣豔萍在湖南漢壽縣被關押期間，以色相&ldquo;擊倒&rdquo;了看守所副所長萬江，萬江曾4次為蔣提供電話與外界聯系，并傳遞信件和字條為蔣串供提供方便。<br />\n<br />\n被稱為&ldquo;三湘第一女巨貪&rdquo;的湖南省建工集團原副總經理蔣豔萍只有初中文化程度，僅用了10多年時間，從一個倉庫保管員升至副廳級的湖南省第六建築工程公司副總經理，貪污斂財達1,000多萬元人民幣（1元人民幣約合0.1536美元）。<br />\n<br />\n蔣豔萍最終因受賄、貪污、介紹賄賂、巨額財產來源不明罪，2001年在湖南被一、二審判處死刑，2003年2月中國最高人民法院改判為死緩。同年3月7日入湖南女子監獄服刑。"},{"pid":"fecaba2a734c51436786d988b43932d1736cad41","tid":513224,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photo.sohu.com/48/08/Img148320848.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphoto.sohu.com%2F48%2F08%2FImg148320848.jpg&h=d37a6ff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgtu.lishiquwen.com/20170525/d306b59c7d40e8ca4c41adafb6132b96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgtu.lishiquwen.com%2F20170525%2Fd306b59c7d40e8ca4c41adafb6132b96.jpg&h=7a38e654&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fc80535adc29b9e73c4b73bc2ac8da15002932b","tid":513224,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T10:08:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"563356185c53771ad8dbb8496056535edcf78160","tid":513224,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"sco